{
  "text": "We compare the performance of our CNN model to that of the best performing reference algorithm for each individual paradigm. For all event-related data analyses (P300 VEP, ERN, MRCP) the reference algorithm is xDAWN Spatial Filtering + Bayesian LDA [CITATION_1] . For oscillatory-based classification of SMR, the reference algorithm is a CSP with covariance matrix regularization [CITATION_2] with a Regularized LDA as used in [CITATION_3] .",
